542
00:44:58,190 --> 00:45:00,270
Đến lúc nói chuyện rồi.

543
00:45:09,780 --> 00:45:11,950
<i>Hail, hail, Blissfield High.</i>

544
00:45:12,030 --> 00:45:14,990
<i>Chomp, chomp, chomp's our battle cry.</i>

545
00:45:15,080 --> 00:45:17,410
<i>When our Beavers come to fight,</i>

546
00:45:17,500 --> 00:45:19,580
<i>feel our glory and our might.</i>

